
As a person looking for a nice roast
I would like to find nearby pubs
And select one that fits the bill for me.

As a person eating a roast
I would like to tell others how good/bad it is
And where they can find it
And when they can eat it
And who made it

As a pub owner
I would like to be able to add my pub to the site
And let people know when we are serving food
And let people know when we are serving food

As a curator of the site
I would like to update and edit details of pubs

As a curator of the site
I would like to edit 

As a user of the site
I would like to be able to add reviews and locations easily using a simple WYSIWYG editor

As a user of the site
I would like to rate peoples reviews, if I agree with them


